.TH Command : GRANT
.s1
The grant command is a means of donating a sector to another
country. To run this command type:
.EX grant 3,-11
The program will request the country number to whom you wish to
donate the sector.
.s1
There are a few restrictions on the use of this command:
.s1
You can not donate a capital or a sanctuary.
You can only offer a sector to an adjacent country, ie. the recipient country
must own a sector next to the sector being sacrificed...
You must own the sector you are donating.

See also : map, spy
